ExtensionFileFilter - Class in scriptmanager.util
Filters files such as BAI, BAM, BED, CDT, FASTA, FA, GFF, TAB for the FileSelection tool based on the extension of the filename.
ExtensionFileFilter(String) - Constructor for class scriptmanager.util.ExtensionFileFilter
Create file filter for the given file extension.
If ExtensionFileFilter is instantiated with "fa", file extensions "fasta" and "fsa" are set to be equivalent.
If ExtensionFileFilter is instantiated with "gff", file extensions "gtf" and "gff3" are set to be equivalent.
ExtensionFileFilter(String, boolean) - Constructor for class scriptmanager.util.ExtensionFileFilter
Create file filter for the given file extension with option to ignore or include ".gz" extensions.
If ExtensionFileFilter is instantiated with "fa", file extensions "fasta" and "fsa" are set to be equivalent.
If ExtensionFileFilter is instantiated with "gff", file extensions "gtf" and "gff3" are set to be equivalent.
